Package zipkin.storage.guava

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GuavaSpanConsumer
    An interface that is equivalent to AsyncSpanConsumer but exposes methods as ListenableFuture to allow asynchronous composition.
    GuavaSpanStore
    An interface that is equivalent to SpanStore but exposes methods as ListenableFuture to allow asynchronous composition.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GuavaStorageAdapters
    Adapters that convert storage components to or from other async libraries.
    GuavaStorageComponent  
    LazyGuavaStorageComponent<S extends GuavaSpanStore,C extends GuavaSpanConsumer>
